{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_33","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated job failed for `dev.zio:zio-internal-macros_2.13:2.1.20`.\n\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-6208-fails-java-run-dev.zio-zio-internal-macros_2.13-2.1.20-594471c0\n\nMost likely failing stage: `native-test-verify` / `generateMetadata`, not the library test itself. The first run failed at `compileTestScala` because the generated test still referenced `zio.internal.TerminalRendering` / `LayerWiringError`, which are no longer accessible in `2.1.20` (`human-intervention-logs/dev.zio:zio-internal-macros_2.13:2.1.20/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-07T07-20-30-094431Z.log`). The preserved branch rewrites the test to cover `zio.internal.ansi`, and later runs succeeded: `gradle-test-2026-05-07T07-24-58-102592Z.log`, `gradle-test-2026-05-07T07-30-43-407193Z.log`, and `gradle-test-2026-05-07T07-31-52-569273Z.log` all end with `BUILD SUCCESSFUL`, while `human-intervention-logs/dev.zio:zio-internal-macros_2.13:2.1.20/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-07T07-27-56-451959Z.log` shows 6/6 tests passing.\n\nThe workflow appears to have failed afterward when generating metadata. `human-intervention-logs/dev.zio:zio-internal-macros_2.13:2.1.20/native-test-verify/cycle-0-generateMetadata-2026-05-07T07-27-50-457181Z.log` reports: `Could not find agent library native-image-agent on the library path, with error: libnative-image-agent.so: cannot open shared object file`. That also explains why dynamic-access coverage is unavailable and why `stats/dev.zio/zio-internal-macros_2.13/2.1.20/execution-metrics.json` is `status: failure` with no metadata/stat artifacts.\n\nPlease inspect:\n- `human-intervention-logs/dev.zio:zio-internal-macros_2.13:2.1.20/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-07T07-20-30-094431Z.log`\n- `human-intervention-logs/dev.zio:zio-internal-macros_2.13:2.1.20/native-test-verify/cycle-0-generateMetadata-2026-05-07T07-27-50-457181Z.log`\n- `human-intervention-logs/dev.zio:zio-internal-macros_2.13:2.1.20/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-07T07-27-56-451959Z.log`\n- `stats/dev.zio/zio-internal-macros_2.13/2.1.20/execution-metrics.json`\n\nManual next steps:\n1. Review the preserved branch diff and confirm the narrowed `zio.internal.ansi` test is acceptable coverage for `2.1.20`.\n2. Re-run `generateMetadata` / native verification in an environment where the GraalVM `native-image-agent` library is present and on the library path.\n3. If that succeeds, regenerate stats/coverage for `2.1.20` and verify the metadata outputs before closing the issue."}}
